    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it since day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like a total dream and feels brand new. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and fall in love with it yourself!",
