    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This specimen features a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal mechanical grip. The powertrain remains in peak factory specification, with rod bearings proactively replaced and throttle actuators serviced to ensure longevity. The chassis benefits from Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing a broad dynamic range from compliant touring to aggressive track-focused damping. Finished in Alpine White over Novillo leather, the cabin exhibits zero bolster compression or trim degradation. The undercarriage is clinically clean, reflecting a life spent in climate-controlled storage with no oxidative stress on the suspension components or subframe. This is a turn-key, collector-quality vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
