    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any creasing or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the mechanical performance is whisper-quiet yet powerful, backed by a comprehensive, specialized service history with every invoice accounted for. Always kept in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car includes all original keys, factory manuals, and documented provenance. It is, quite simply, as close to a brand-new vehicle as you can find on the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
