      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with the precision of a new machine, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our uncompromising standards for excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire an investment-grade example that defies its age.",
