    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been totally pampered since day one\u2014truly in pristine, showroom condition. Not a single scratch or dent in sight, and the interior still feels and smells fresh. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
