    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), featuring the highly desirable 3.8L 9A1 direct-injection flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerhouse delivers 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-fitted limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping characteristics for both high-speed stability and cornering precision. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc aluminum fixed calipers over cross-drilled rotors, exhibiting zero fade. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, with a documented service history confirming the integrity of the cooling system and drivetrain. Flawless original paint and a pristine interior make this an exceptional example for the discerning purist.",
